data.description: FANTASTIC 3/2 family home on 1.4 acres with in-ground pool and fabulous pool house. This brick home features 2 living areas, one with special ceiling and fireplace, the other with beautiful large windows and hardwood floors. The kitchen boasts granite counter tops, new light fixtures and INCLUDES all appliances! New paint freshens up this home making if feel light and airy. The closed in breezeway is precious and provides for the perfect place for coffee or tea. It connects to the pool house which has a fireplace, full bath and full kitchen. PLENTY of room for the kids, guests or make it a rental! Large pool-side entertaining area in the fenced in back yard. The ac/heat pump is 1 year old inside and out, did I mention the land? You have a large cleared lot next to the house. Keep it for a buffer or build your dream shop! So much to see here. Call today!
